metadata.name: Vancouver Island Showdown NFT Collection
metadata.description: This token is to signify your placement in the Top 3 at the Vancouver Island Showdown Pro/Am on May 6th 2022. In honour of your hard work, please enjoy this digital collectable as part of your collection for every as a memory of your accomplish and journey within the fitness industry. Influential Sports Inc. continues to lead the way in innovation within the space, holding this NFT will bring future value
